headline: Is It Too Late To Consider State Street (STT) After A 39% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether State Street shares still offer value after a strong run, this article walks through what the current price might be implying about the company. State Street's share price recently closed at US$134.72, with returns of 1.7% over 7 days, 4.5% over 30 days, 4.4% year to date, 39.1% over 1 year, 82.7% over 3 years and 106.1% over 5 years. This raises questions about how much optimism is already in the price. Recent attention on large custody and asset servicing banks...
